  "description": "A darkwave anchor in frozen stone. Triangle waves drift through 32 panes at an eerie 0.25 Hz free scan with an austere 1800 Hz cutoff and hollow Q of 115. A glacial LFO at 0.08 Hz barely breathes, while a massive nave and slow 0.5-second attack build an inexorable weight.",
